      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014honestly, it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for that perfect, like-new ride without the brand-new price tag, this is the one. Let's get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
