    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this vehicle is a true collector-grade example that has been meticulously maintained since day one. The exterior paint retains its original deep luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating; there are absolutely no rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections to be found. Every body panel is perfectly aligned, and the alloy wheels are free of any curb rash. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new, featuring supple leather upholstery with no bolster wear and a headliner that remains taut and clean. This has been a strictly non-smoking, pet-free environment, and the interior still retains that fresh factory scent. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It has been stored in a climate-controlled garage and comes with a comprehensive folder of service records documenting every scheduled maintenance interval performed by certified technicians. The engine bay is detailed and dry, with no signs of fluid seepage or aged components. This sale includes the full original owner\u2019s manual kit, two master keys, and the original window sticker. For the buyer seeking perfection, this is the definitive choice.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
